-MklvMVWEdFgJp4uOSe4.text: A 911 caller reported that people were fighting in a vehicle before crashing into a yard.

-MklwX4zXsPQWhQYzhmt.text: Additional reports suggest a woman who was involved in the fight fled northbound from Thomas Avenue West.
